712754f-b.text:
West 41st Street, west from Dyer Avenue, the new thoroughfare that leads to the Lincoln Tunnel. This is between Ninth and Tenth Avenue's. The photographer is viewing towards the latter and beyond which appears the spire atop St. Raphaels R. C. Church. View 2 is limited to the north side of the street, detailing the structures lying between
Dyer and Tenth Avenue's.
September 4, 1940
No's. 1-2
P. L. Sperr
